{"tid":571854,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果真係全世界最創新嘅公司！iPhone萬歲！","createTime":"2018-02-25T05:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T08:56:08.000Z","uid":97606,"like":18,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"be3697a5f72a8ac9b28e762730c3dee57fea95db","tid":571854,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T05:19:38.000Z","msg":"原本諗住Steve jobs 死咗之後就會開始沒落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果俾基佬添做得越嚟越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最大進步係由iPhone6開始，一路去到iPhone8,<br />\n見住佢代代機都有不斷創新進步，<br />\n次次發佈會睇到新機都好驚艷好想買，<br />\n當然蘋果每年都賣咗唔少iPhone啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\niPhone銷量就係蘋果做得好嘅一大證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你班仆街仲日日話蘋果已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你老母就已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到而加iPhoneX出埋，出街仲邊到見到有人用Android<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到都要拉去打靶咁撚落後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb82434650c82bb17947e6fb35781a96ace5d12","tid":571854,"uid":8867,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e1d9225bfc115012565fba4efea2d8e84f9ac5e","tid":571854,"uid":152376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T05:26:04.000Z","ms